JCoin Privacy Policy

Last updated: June 1, 2023

1. Introduction
Welcome to JCoin ("we," "our," or "us"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you about how we look after your personal data when you visit our website or use our app and tell you about your privacy rights.

2. Information We Collect
We collect several types of information from and about users of our app, including:

Personal identifiers (name, email address)
Account information (username, password)
Usage data (videos watched, rewards earned)
Device information (IP address, device type, operating system)
3. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect about you to:

Provide, maintain, and improve our services
Process transactions and manage your account
Send notifications related to your account or activity
Analyze usage patterns and optimize user experience
Comply with legal obligations
4. Sharing Your Information
We may share your information with:

Service providers who perform services on our behalf
Advertisers and advertising networks
Analytics providers
Law enforcement or other governmental agencies when required by law
5. Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.

6. User Rights
Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information, including:

Right to access your personal data
Right to correct inaccurate data
Right to delete your data
Right to restrict processing
Right to data portability
7. Contact Information
If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our practices, please contact us at:
Email: privacy@jcoin.app
Address: 123 Main Street, Anytown, USA 12345
